headline: Nvidia Earnings, PPI: What to Watch Next Week
summary: Investors next week will focus on a quarterly update from Nvidia, whose results have become a bellwether for the broader artificial-intelligence trade. They also will assess the health of the American consumer through confidence data and earnings from home-improvement retailers Home Depot and Lowe’s.

headline: Western Alliance Bank Supports OnQ With $7.5 Million Asset-Based Line of Credit
summary: NEW YORK, February 20, 2026--Western Alliance Bank today announced that OnQ, the leading retail display company, has secured an enhanced credit facility with the bank’s Asset-Based Lending Group.
